com.github.dandelion.core.bundle.loader.spi
Class AbstractBundleLoader

java.lang.Object
  com.github.dandelion.core.bundle.loader.spi.AbstractBundleLoader
All Implemented Interfaces:
BundleLoader
Direct Known Subclasses:
DandelionBundleLoader, VendorBundleLoader
public abstract class AbstractBundleLoader
extends Object
implements BundleLoader

Abstract bundle loader in charge of loading JSON definitions of bundle.

The JSON definitions are scanned in the folder specified by the getPath() method.

The lookup is recursive depending on the BundleLoader.isRecursive() return value.

Since:
0.10.0
Author:
Romain Lespinasse, Thibault Duchateau
